<view class="challenge-index">

<view class="banner-section">
  <image class="banner-img" src="https://images-1408449839.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/images/knowledge/knowledge1.jpg" mode="widthFix"></image>
  <view class="banner-title">环保知识大闯关</view>
  <view class="banner-subtitle">测一测你的垃圾分类段位</view>
</view>

<view class="stats-card">
  <view class="stats-item">
    <text class="stats-label">当前称号</text>
    <text class="stats-value {{titleClass}}">{{userTitle}}</text>
  </view>
  <view class="divider"></view>
  <view class="stats-item">
    <text class="stats-label">累计环保星</text>
    <text class="stats-value score-highlight">{{userScore}}</text>
  </view>
</view>

<view class="leaderboard-entry-card" bindtap="goToLeaderboard">
  <view class="entry-left">
    <text class="entry-icon">🏆</text>
    <text class="entry-title">环保闯关光荣榜</text>
  </view>
  <view class="entry-right">
    <text class="entry-sub">查看当前排名</text>
    <text class="entry-arrow">></text>
  </view>
</view>

<view class="rules-card">
  <view class="rules-title">📜 挑战与奖励规则</view>
  <view class="rule-line">
    <text class="rule-dot"></text>
    <text>【经典闯关】共 10 题，慢慢想不着急。只要完成就能获得 1 颗环保星🌟，全对可获得「完美通关」评级，最高拿到 2 颗环保星！</text>
  </view>
  <view class="rule-line">
    <text class="rule-dot"></text>
    <text>【极限60秒】限时 60 秒大挑战！保底 1 颗环保星，又快又准最高可拿 3 颗环保星，还能获得炫酷的「闪电小超人」称号哦！</text>
  </view>
  <view class="rule-line">
    <text class="rule-dot"></text>
    <text>【每日打卡】每天第一次完成任何挑战，都能额外获得 2 朵小红花🌺，快攒起来去校园小卖部换礼物吧！</text>
  </view>
</view>

<view class="action-section">
  <view class="mode-btn classic-btn" bindtap="goToQuiz" data-mode="classic">
    <text class="btn-title">经典闯关</text>
    <text class="btn-sub">稳扎稳打，巩固知识</text>
  </view>
  
  <view class="mode-btn timed-btn" bindtap="goToQuiz" data-mode="timed">
    <text class="btn-title">极限60秒</text>
    <text class="btn-sub">高风险高回报，挑战极限</text>
  </view>
</view>
</view>